{"tid":1191651,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"黃絲：小心有人搞事，遇有事請合力影抵搞事者容貌！","createTime":"2019-06-08T04:53:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-08T11:18:48.000Z","uid":219007,"like":10,"dislike":243,"uniUserReply":40,"replies":[{"pid":"7c1935b434602a5cf7c798eae56fbdbfb3c807c0","tid":1191651,"uid":219007,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-08T04:53:51.000Z","msg":"岩先一打開蘋果底下comment<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n九成小心有鬼，呼籲篤灰<br />\n<br />\n得一個反割席<br />\n<br />\n&lsquo;全民上街 溫馨提示 記得帶水和紙扇 開著電話錄影功能 和gopro 因近日事件相信有可能有有心人搞事煽動 挑釁 如有事發生請大家合力影低搞事者面貌和發生過程作不時之需&rsquo;<br />\n<br />\n&lsquo;注意安全，一旦有人搞事，好容易發生人踩人事件，遊行時，請帶備止血藥及清洗傷口的清水。&rsquo;<br />\n<br />\n&lsquo;要注意身边有人尊登搞事，比我見別實屌九佢。&rsquo;<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/105259197447/posts/10157725941782448/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F105259197447%2Fposts%2F10157725941782448%2F&d=Bm7f%2FS52JQW29R4IancW88LrQrhaJullgCUoYOUuTa8%3D&h=e7883bd2\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/105259197447/posts/10157725941782448/</a>"},{"pid":"afbaf3d99893666c4a85b04823c8e82fa3f284b3","tid":1191651,"uid":42340,"like":15,"dislike":131,"score":-116,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2019-06-08T04:55:02.000Z","msg":"犯法比人拉有咩問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wfc2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1a87484ea944204db8f0edb10e0f414d3420dd22","tid":1191651,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-08T04:55:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"91109cd20598ac53830df21432358d1bc08f6029","tid":1191651,"uid":219007,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-08T04:59:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3802bb17be46158decb77df5765ef1f847af8d80","tid":1191651,"uid":219007,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-08T05:04:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets